你從沒談過戀愛 怎麼知道這是愛？
How do you know it's love if you've never been in love before?

516
01:01:06,850 --> 01:01:09,610
因為我感覺到
'Cause I feel it.

517
01:01:09,780 --> 01:01:11,270
哪堙H
Where?

518
01:01:14,990 --> 01:01:16,820
在我肚子堙K
In my stomach.

519
01:01:19,830 --> 01:01:23,190
暖暖的
It's all warm.

520
01:01:23,360 --> 01:01:28,490
以前我老是胃痛 但現在沒有了
I always had a knot there, and now it's gone.

521
01:01:31,500 --> 01:01:36,670
瑪蒂達，我很高興你不再胃痛了
Mathilda, I'm glad you don't have a stomachache anymore.

522
01:01:36,840 --> 01:01:39,210
但那並不代表什麼
I don't think it means anything.

523
01:01:39,350 --> 01:01:43,110
我要遲到了 我討厭工作時遲到
I'm late for work. I hate being late for work.

524
01:02:27,660 --> 01:02:29,560
你女兒的小提琴練得怎樣了？
How's the practicing going?

525
01:02:59,630 --> 01:03:04,650
- 今天過得好嗎，小姐？ - 我有點厭倦練習了
- How are we today, miss? - A little sick of practicing.

526
01:03:04,800 --> 01:03:06,630
我了解
I understand.

527
01:03:06,800 --> 01:03:08,630
但你做得不錯
But you're doing all right.

528
01:03:08,800 --> 01:03:10,710
我沒有接到任何投訴
I haven't received any complaints.

529
01:03:10,720 --> 01:03:15,340
我在弦上放塊布減少噪音
I put a cloth over the strings to lessen the noise.

530
01:03:16,240 --> 01:03:17,680
那真聰明
That's very smart.

531
01:03:17,880 --> 01:03:22,410
- 不是所有人都愛音樂 - 我知道
- Not everyone loves music. - I know.

532
01:03:22,580 --> 01:03:24,610
你父親到底是做什麼的？
What does your father do?

533
01:03:26,120 --> 01:03:30,490
- 他是個作曲家 - 真了不起
- He's a composer. - That's wonderful.

534
01:03:30,660 --> 01:03:33,130
他其實不是我父親
Except he's not really my father.

535
01:03:38,800 --> 01:03:40,430
他是我的愛人
He's my lover.

536
01:03:44,610 --> 01:03:47,840
我要去散步
Think I'll go for a walk.

537
01:04:02,660 --> 01:04:06,150
- 星期六晚上你要做什麼？ - 共進晚餐好嗎？
- What are you doing Saturday night? - What about dinner?

538
01:04:06,330 --> 01:04:09,320
- 嘿，你要去哪堙H - 探訪6樓J室的朋友
- Where you going? - Visiting friends at 6J .

539
01:04:09,530 --> 01:04:11,290
好，去吧 星期六怎麼樣？
Go ahead. What about Saturday?

540
01:04:11,430 --> 01:04:15,300
- 晚上八點？ - 我不知道
- About 8:00? - I don't know.

541
01:04:15,470 --> 01:04:19,460
你已經有約了？
You got plans?

542
01:04:24,980 --> 01:04:26,740
在這婺I頭？
Meet you here?

543
01:05:41,860 --> 01:05:44,350
我們知道你是個忙人 我們會長話短說
We know you're a busy man. We'll make this short.

544
01:05:44,360 --> 01:05:48,660
你只須說清楚當天發生的一切
If you'll just take us step-by-step through exactly what happened.

545
01:05:49,500 --> 01:05:52,230
那人站在這堙A取出槍來
The guy was here. He went for his gun.

546
01:05:52,400 --> 01:05:54,490
我們就向他開槍
Bang, we shot him.

547
01:05:57,910 --> 01:06:00,740
- 那些小孩當時在哪堙H - 我不知道！
- Where exactly were the kids? - I don't know!

548
01:06:00,910 --> 01:06:03,310
他們應該在學校堙A不是嗎？
They should have been at school, don't you think?

549
01:06:03,480 --> 01:06:05,310
你證詞說你是第一個到達的人
Your statement said you were the first man in.

550
01:06:05,480 --> 01:06:07,380
- 你沒看見有小孩嗎？ - 門被砸壞了
- Didn't you see any kids? - The door was broken.

551
01:06:07,580 --> 01:06:09,550
發生什麼事了？ 你有依照程序辦事嗎？
What happened? Did you follow the procedure?

552
01:06:11,750 --> 01:06:15,210
我失去了一個好弟兄 你們他媽的要我怎麼樣？
I lost a good man here. What the fuck do you want with me?

553
01:06:15,420 --> 01:06:17,760
要你合作
Cooperation.

554
01:06:20,760 --> 01:06:24,930
我沒時間談這些無聊的廢話！
I haven't got time for this Mickey Mouse bullshit!

555
01:06:24,940 --> 01:06:29,460
你們想要我合作？ 到我辦公室來，4602室
You want cooperation? Come up in my office, room 4602.

556
01:06:40,690 --> 01:06:42,680
孩子們應該到學校去
Kids should be at school.

557
01:06:44,020 --> 01:06:46,510
拜托，那是我的球！
Come on, that's my ball!

558
01:06:46,690 --> 01:06:51,090
還給我 你要去哪堙H
Give that back. Where you going?

559
01:06:51,300 --> 01:06:54,630
該死！你要去哪堙H 那是我的球！
Damn! Where you going, man? That's my ball!

560
01:07:01,440 --> 01:07:03,570
跟著那輛藍色的車
Follow the blue car.

561
01:07:03,640 --> 01:07:06,600
你要我開響音樂和闖紅燈嗎？
You want me to blast the music and go through the lights?

562
01:07:06,680 --> 01:07:08,350
不，慢慢開
No, drive slowly.

563
01:07:08,380 --> 01:07:11,610
一百塊拿去，閉上你的狗嘴，好嗎？
Take the hundred bucks, and shut the fuck up.

564
01:07:44,080 --> 01:07:47,880
我不想跟你斗 但你逼得我別無選擇
I do not want to fight you, but you leave me no choice.

565
01:07:49,650 --> 01:07:54,260
孩子，你讓我茅塞頓開！
Boy, you just gave me a great idea!

566
01:07:57,960 --> 01:08:01,290
- 有了好主意！ - 歡迎收看每日娛樂新聞…
- I mean a big one! - Welcome back to E! News Daily...

567
01:08:01,300 --> 01:08:04,230
我們30分鍾的最新娛樂報導
our 30-minute look at the latest in entertainment news.

568
01:08:04,370 --> 01:08:06,200
我是碧安卡法拉
I'm Bianca Ferrar.

569
01:08:10,980 --> 01:08:14,240
送給你的，一件禮物
It's for you. A present.

570
01:08:16,180 --> 01:08:19,990
你要我打開嗎？ 我來打開吧
Do you want me to open it? I'll open it.

571
01:08:24,720 --> 01:08:28,280
你喜歡嗎？ 很漂亮，是嗎？
How do you like it? Nice, eh?

572
01:08:28,460 --> 01:08:30,290
麥葛芬先生？
Mr. McGuffin?

573
01:08:32,830 --> 01:08:35,300
我能跟你談談嗎？
Can I have a word with you?

574
01:09:55,720 --> 01:09:58,940
這是報酬，兩萬元，對嗎？
Here. It's for a contract. Twenty grand, right?

575
01:09:58,950 --> 01:10:02,040
他名叫諾曼·史丹菲爾德 他在緝毒署…
His name is Norman Stansfield, and he's in room 4602...

576
01:10:02,050 --> 01:10:04,960
4602室，聯邦廣場26號
in the D.E.A. building, 26 Federal Plaza.

577
01:10:05,960 --> 01:10:08,390
- 我不接受 - 為什麼？
- I'm not taking it. - Why not?

578
01:10:09,360 --> 01:10:11,450
- 我幹不了 - 那好吧
- It's too heavy. - Well.

579
01:10:11,460 --> 01:10:13,190
你能把你的槍租給我一天嗎？
Will you rent me your gear for the day?

580
01:10:13,400 --> 01:10:15,920
我從不出借我的槍
I never lend out my gear.

581
01:10:16,070 --> 01:10:17,830
但…
But...

582
01:10:17,970 --> 01:10:19,840
你可以用你自己的槍
you still have your gun. Use it.

583
01:10:20,010 --> 01:10:23,630
幫我個忙，不要向窗外亂射
Just do me a favor. Don't shoot out the window.

584
01:10:23,640 --> 01:10:25,940
你為什麼要這樣對我？
Why are you so mean to me?

585
01:10:27,580 --> 01:10:30,170
瘋狂地去殺你毫不在乎的人…
Wildly killing people you don't give a shit about...

586
01:10:30,180 --> 01:10:34,190
卻不肯去殺那些 殺了我全家的混蛋？
but you won't get the bastards that killed my whole family?

587
01:10:34,520 --> 01:10:37,280
相信我，複仇不是件好事
Revenge is not good once you're done. Believe.

588
01:10:38,160 --> 01:10:40,650
- 最好是忘掉仇恨 - 忘掉？
- It's better to forget. - Forget?

589
01:10:40,790 --> 01:10:43,690
在我看見我弟弟的屍體 在地板上的輪廓後…
After I've seen the outline of my brother's body on the floor...

590
01:10:43,860 --> 01:10:45,760
你期望我忘掉？
you expect me to forget?

591
01:10:45,930 --> 01:10:48,160
我要殺死那些狗雜種
I want to kill those sons of bitches.

592
01:10:48,170 --> 01:10:50,200
打爛他們的腦袋
Blow their fucking heads off.

593
01:10:50,300 --> 01:10:53,170
你殺了人以後，一切都不一樣了
Nothing's the same after you've killed someone.

594
01:10:55,070 --> 01:10:58,340
你的生活會永遠改變
Your life is changed forever.

595
01:10:59,680 --> 01:11:03,480
今後你睡覺時 都得睜著一只眼睛
You have to sleep with one eye open for the rest of your life.

596
01:11:03,650 --> 01:11:06,240
我不在乎睡什麼覺，堜
I don't give a shit about sleeping, Leon.

597
01:11:07,290 --> 01:11:09,250
我想要愛…
I want love...

598
01:11:09,690 --> 01:11:11,490
或者死亡
or death.

599
01:11:12,530 --> 01:11:14,080
就是這樣
That's it.

600
01:11:15,900 --> 01:11:17,990
我想要死亡
I want death.

601
01:11:18,630 --> 01:11:21,860
別來煩我了，瑪蒂達 我已經厭倦了你的遊戲
Get off my case, Mathilda. I'm tired of your games.

602
01:11:25,740 --> 01:11:27,800
這遊戲真的很棒，堜
There's this really great game, Leon.

603
01:11:27,970 --> 01:11:31,370
它讓人變得更好，讓人開始思考
Makes people nicer. Starts them thinking.

604
01:11:35,780 --> 01:11:38,110
你喜歡的那種遊戲
The kind of game you love.

605
01:11:50,560 --> 01:11:52,290
如果我贏了…
If I win...

606
01:11:53,430 --> 01:11:56,270
你得讓我跟著你…一輩子
you keep me with you... for life.

607
01:11:58,470 --> 01:12:00,030
如果你輸了呢？
And if you lose?

608
01:12:00,210 --> 01:12:03,540
你和以前一樣，自己去買東西
Go shopping alone, like before.

609
01:12:05,710 --> 01:12:08,110
你會輸的，瑪蒂達
You're gonna lose, Mathilda.

610
01:12:09,820 --> 01:12:12,750
槍膛埵酗@顆子彈，我聽出來了
There's a round in the chamber. I heard it.

611
01:12:12,760 --> 01:12:13,980
那又怎樣？
So what?

612
01:12:14,150 --> 01:12:17,620
如果我腦袋中槍死了，你會怎樣？
What's it to you if I end up with a bullet in the head?

613
01:12:19,960 --> 01:12:21,430
沒什麼
Nothing.

614
01:12:25,370 --> 01:12:27,880
我希望你沒說謊，堜
I hope you're not lying, Leon.

615
01:12:28,900 --> 01:12:32,130
我真的希望 你內心深處也沒有愛過我
I really hope that deep down inside there's no love in you.

616
01:12:35,310 --> 01:12:37,210
因為如果你…
Because if there is...

617
01:12:37,380 --> 01:12:40,930
有那麼一點點愛我的話…
just a little bit of love in there for me...

618
01:12:42,980 --> 01:12:46,390
那麼幾分鍾後，你就會後悔 從沒說出自己真正的感受
I think that in a few minutes you'll regret you never said anything.

619
01:12:56,000 --> 01:12:57,900
我愛你，堜
I love you, Leon.

620
01:13:15,020 --> 01:13:16,710
我贏了
I win.

621
01:13:33,930 --> 01:13:36,270
我受傷了
I took a hit.

622
01:13:37,070 --> 01:13:39,400
現在我需要個幫手
I need a hand now.

623
01:13:39,570 --> 01:13:43,570
我知道她還很小，但她學得很快
I know she's young, but she learns fast.

624
01:13:43,740 --> 01:13:46,400
小孩需要培養，對嗎？
Kids need to be shaped into something, right?

625
01:13:46,450 --> 01:13:49,580
我知道，那是我教你的 但是難道沒有年齡限制嗎？
I know. I taught you that. But ain't there an age limit?

626
01:13:49,620 --> 01:13:51,180
她已經18歲了
She's 18.

627
01:13:51,350 --> 01:13:53,180
真的嗎？
Really?

628
01:13:56,990 --> 01:13:59,050
來點喝的好嗎，湯尼？
How about something to drink, Tony?

629
01:13:59,130 --> 01:14:02,330
好的，馬諾洛，給堜蠿茠M牛奶
Sure. Manolo, glass of milk for Leon.

630
01:14:04,970 --> 01:14:06,800
不錯的刺青
Nice tattoo.

631
01:14:11,540 --> 01:14:14,870
馬諾洛，兩杯牛奶
Manolo, make that two.

632
01:14:34,500 --> 01:14:37,190
- 幹嘛要戴帽子？ - 我可不能感冒
- What's that for? - Can't afford to catch cold.

633
01:14:38,370 --> 01:14:40,270
首先，找出門鏈在哪
First you find out where the chain is.

634
01:14:40,430 --> 01:14:43,700
雖然看不見，但你能感覺得到 這
You can't see it, but you can feel it. Here.

635
01:14:43,800 --> 01:14:46,830
- 我按門鈴，你跟他說話 - 我該說些什麼？
- I'll ring, you start talking. - What do I say?

636
01:14:47,540 --> 01:14:49,270
隨你喜歡
Whatever you want.

637
01:14:51,410 --> 01:14:53,240
- 誰？ - 嗨
- Yes? - Hi.

638
01:14:53,410 --> 01:14:55,250
我是蘇珊
It's Susan.

639
01:14:55,420 --> 01:14:58,840
抱歉，你一定是找錯門了，小姑娘
I'm sorry. You must have the wrong door, little girl.

640
01:14:58,890 --> 01:15:01,020
我不認識什麼蘇珊
I don't know any Susan.

641
01:15:01,190 --> 01:15:05,150
退後點，我什麼都看不見
Move back a little. I can't see anything.

642
01:15:05,330 --> 01:15:07,820
走道的燈沒開
The light's out.

643
01:15:08,000 --> 01:15:10,130
外面一片漆黑
It's all dark out here.

644
01:15:13,230 --> 01:15:18,240
- 先生，我很害怕 - 好吧
- Mister, I'm scared. - Okay.

645
01:15:22,380 --> 01:15:25,000
你他媽的想幹什麼？
What the fuck are you doing?

646
01:15:30,350 --> 01:15:31,880
張開嘴
Open up.

647
01:15:33,450 --> 01:15:36,620
如果它離開了你嘴巴 我就扣扳機，明白了嗎？
If it leaves your mouth, I'll pull the trigger, capisce?

648
01:16:14,060 --> 01:16:16,540
沒問題了，把嘴挪開
Here's okay. Let it go.

649
01:16:16,620 --> 01:16:18,660
我說：「把嘴挪開」
I said, Let it go.

650
01:16:18,830 --> 01:16:21,130
走，到那邊去
Move. Move over.

651
01:16:22,770 --> 01:16:24,170
放輕松
Easy. Easy.

652
01:16:24,340 --> 01:16:27,170
小心點，你想要我…
Easy. Careful. You want me--

653
01:16:28,810 --> 01:16:31,440
上吧，輪到你了
Go ahead. Your turn.

654
01:16:38,490 --> 01:16:40,850
救命，求你別殺我
Help me. Please don't beat me.

655
01:16:41,020 --> 01:16:43,490
先生？
Sir?

656
01:16:46,660 --> 01:16:48,980
先生，那些白粉不是我的
Sir, it's not my dope.

657
01:16:49,070 --> 01:16:51,030
先生，聽著，我…
Sir, look I--

658
01:16:51,110 --> 01:16:52,980
請往左邊一點
A little left, please.

659
01:16:56,270 --> 01:16:57,700
在開槍之前…
Before-- Ple--

660
01:17:00,470 --> 01:17:03,870
現在再開一槍，確保目標死亡
Now, the security shot.

661
01:17:08,220 --> 01:17:11,280
不，第二槍要射在胸口上方
No, the second goes higher on the chest.

662
01:17:11,450 --> 01:17:13,720
瞄准心髒和肺
Aim for the heart and lungs.

663
01:17:13,890 --> 01:17:15,790
就是那堙A明白了嗎？
There. Right there. You see?

664
01:17:15,990 --> 01:17:18,130
第一槍打倒目標
The first shot takes him out of order.

665
01:17:18,190 --> 01:17:20,790
- 第二槍就解決他 - 你們他媽的在幹什麼？
- The second finishes him off. - What are you fucking doing?

666
01:17:20,960 --> 01:17:22,360
千萬別射臉
Never in the face.

667
01:17:22,530 --> 01:17:25,660
如果目標無法辨認 你就拿不到酬金
If they can't recognize the client, you don't get paid.

668
01:17:25,830 --> 01:17:29,400
因為你可以隨便找個替死鬼來交差
You could take out anybody and said you did the job.

669
01:17:29,540 --> 01:17:32,130
- 明白了嗎？ - 明白了，別射臉
- Got it? - Got it. Never in the face.

670
01:17:32,340 --> 01:17:35,710
- 現在你可以把槍收起來 - 你們在幹什麼？
- Now you can put the tools away. - What are you fucking doing?

671
01:17:35,840 --> 01:17:38,440
這到底是怎麼回事？ 嘿，先生！
What the fuck is going on? Hey, mister!

672
01:17:38,480 --> 01:17:40,680
你們…
What are you fucking--

673
01:17:43,820 --> 01:17:46,380
如果經常用消音器的話…
You see, when you use the silencer a lot...

674
01:17:46,560 --> 01:17:48,720
你要在這堜騅竷活K
you have to put a piece of cloth here...

675
01:17:48,890 --> 01:17:51,690
因為發熱會使堶捫N起來
because it gets very hot and could burn it inside.

676
01:17:51,860 --> 01:17:54,490
最好是塊濕布，黑色的布
A damp, black cloth is the best.

677
01:17:57,930 --> 01:17:59,760
你在做什麼？
What you doing?

678
01:17:59,940 --> 01:18:03,060
我們說過，不殺女人和小孩
We said no women, no kids.

679
01:18:03,240 --> 01:18:06,830
你以為這些東西會害死誰 那些癮君子嗎？
Who do you think this is gonna kill, junkies and monkeys?

680
01:18:22,520 --> 01:18:25,070
毒物都清理完畢了
Now it's clean.

681
01:18:25,890 --> 01:18:28,590
我們走吧
Let's get out of here.

682
