02:02:54,780 --> 02:02:58,740
比銀行更好 因為銀行會被打劫
it's better than a bank 'cause banks always get knocked off.

1027
02:02:58,910 --> 02:03:01,510
但沒人敢打劫老湯尼
No one knocks off old Tony.

1028
02:03:01,680 --> 02:03:04,240
但這是你的錢，在這期間…
But it's your money. In the meantime...

1029
02:03:04,420 --> 02:03:08,250
你只須偶爾來一趟…
all you gotta do is come here every once in awhile...

1030
02:03:08,420 --> 02:03:12,090
我會給你一點錢，讓你玩樂一下
and I'll dish it out so you can have a little fun.

1031
02:03:13,330 --> 02:03:14,660
拿去
Here.

1032
02:03:14,800 --> 02:03:20,390
- 先給你一百塊 - 不能給我一個工作嗎？
- Here's a hundred bucks to start. - Can't I get a job instead?

1033
02:03:20,400 --> 02:03:25,390
工作？你能做什麼？
A job? What the hell can you do?

1034
02:03:25,400 --> 02:03:27,440
我會做「清潔工作」
I can clean.

1035
02:03:28,610 --> 02:03:31,380
我沒有工作給十二歲的小孩做…
I ain't got no work for a 12-year-old kid...

1036
02:03:31,380 --> 02:03:33,310
別再有這種荒唐的想法了！
so get it out of your goddamn head!

1037
02:03:33,320 --> 02:03:36,180
結束了！遊戲結束了！
It's over! The game's over!

1038
02:03:36,220 --> 02:03:38,750
堜蠾漱F！
Leon's dead!

1039
02:03:38,890 --> 02:03:40,750
你聽到了嗎？
You hear me?

1040
02:03:48,260 --> 02:03:52,690
拜托，你以為我不傷心嗎？
Come on. You think I ain't hurting too?

1041
02:03:58,310 --> 02:04:00,600
但他已經死了
But he's dead.

1042
02:04:00,780 --> 02:04:05,940
你應該忘掉這一切，回學校去 明白嗎？
You're gonna forget all this craziness and get your little ass back to school.

1043
02:04:05,980 --> 02:04:09,170
現在拿著錢，離開這
Now take this money and get the hell outta here.

1044
02:04:09,250 --> 02:04:11,340
下個月前別再讓我看到你…
Don't let me see your face till next month...

1045
02:04:11,420 --> 02:04:15,480
因為我快失去耐性了
'cause something tells me I'm about to lose my famous kind streak.

1046
02:05:06,840 --> 02:05:10,210
我的父母…
My parents...

1047
02:05:10,380 --> 02:05:12,370
都死了…
died...

1048
02:05:12,550 --> 02:05:17,040
四周前死於一場車禍
in a car accident four weeks ago.

1049
02:05:17,220 --> 02:05:19,050
太可怕了
It was terrible.

1050
02:05:21,690 --> 02:05:25,540
你剛來的時候 我們沒時間互相了解…
We didn't have the time to get to know one another when you first came here...

1051
02:05:25,550 --> 02:05:30,490
但我要你明白 我不是會讓孩子失望的女人…
but I want you to know I'm not the kind of woman who'd let down a child...

1052
02:05:30,570 --> 02:05:33,600
無論她處境如何 無論她犯了什麼錯
whatever her situation, whatever her mistake.

1053
02:05:33,770 --> 02:05:39,230
所以我會盡力幫助你 歡迎你回來
So I'm going to help you and do my best to welcome you here again.

1054
02:05:40,740 --> 02:05:43,300
但有個條件…
But on one condition:

1055
02:05:43,480 --> 02:05:46,570
你必須停止對我說謊，瑪蒂達
You have to stop lying to me, Mathilda.

1056
02:05:46,750 --> 02:05:48,810
我要你試著…
I want you to take a chance...

1057
02:05:49,280 --> 02:05:51,820
信任我
and trust me.

1058
02:05:51,950 --> 02:05:54,390
告訴我，你究竟發生了什麼事
Tell me what happened to you.

1059
02:05:55,650 --> 02:05:56,700
好吧
Okay.

1060
02:05:57,870 --> 02:06:01,040
我的家人因為毒品問題…
My family got shot down by D.E.A. officers...

1061
02:06:01,080 --> 02:06:04,500
被緝毒署的人殺了
because of a drug problem.

1062
02:06:04,540 --> 02:06:07,210
我和世上最棒的男人一起離開
I left with the greatest guy on Earth.

1063
02:06:07,250 --> 02:06:12,050
他是城堻抭誚y的殺手 但他今天早上死了
He was a hit man, the best in town, but he died this morning.

1064
02:06:12,090 --> 02:06:15,970
你不幫我的話 今晚我也會死的
If you don't help me, I'll be dead by tonight.

1065
02:06:36,360 --> 02:06:38,330
- 你們認識她嗎？ - 不認識
- You know her? - No.

1066
02:06:38,360 --> 02:06:39,430
我從沒見過她
I've never seen her.

1067
02:07:05,600 --> 02:07:08,260
我想我們在這媟|好好的，堜
I think we'll be okay here, Leon.
